    {
      "id": "pes50CCQvt9pe3EZ3LO_6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1338.6192990014686,
      "y": 81097.04328546129,
      "width": 1056,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c00G",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1413405853,
      "version": 372,
      "versionNonce": 1741778141,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777705102214,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "we have retrieve the data on the basis of vector this is called retrieval phase\nonce we have retrieved data, then passing retrieved data and query to our LLM is called\naugment phase, on the basis of this LLM need to generate output this is called Generation phase.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "we have retrieve the data on the basis of vector this is called retrieval phase\nonce we have retrieved data, then passing retrieved data and query to our LLM is called\naugment phase, on the basis of this LLM need to generate output this is called Generation phase.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zlCEUzbTQVM5uJm-7iXJD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1332.4708615014686,
      "y": 81275.57453546129,
      "width": 319,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c00H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 253805245,
      "version": 31,
      "versionNonce": 1026548317,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777708673552,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Which  Vector DB we will use?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Which  Vector DB we will use?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "K7T2bcnLF5JysxnX2NbIR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1372.8575802514686,
      "y": 81316.92219171129,
      "width": 330,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c00I",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1867951901,
      "version": 40,
      "versionNonce": 2040655411,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777708770841,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "we will use pinecon, using API",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "we will use pinecon, using API",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KhvjVUfyDUAYD3h3WuK0R",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1327.3458615014686,
      "y": 81440.26594171129,
      "width": 979,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c00J",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1755977491,
      "version": 470,
      "versionNonce": 80043133,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777709746074,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "phase 1 ->\n    PDF load\n\nphase 2 ->\n    chunking\n\nphase 3 ->\n    convert each chunk into vector, this is done by our embedding models like LLM\n\nphase4 ->\n    store them in Vector DB(pinecone)\n\nHere we need to use diff diff things in each phase, for pdf we need to have pdf loader,\nfor chunking we should have chunking model, for converting each chunk into vector we need\nto use something else.\nWe can make them easy by using Langchain\n    ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "phase 1 ->\n    PDF load\n\nphase 2 ->\n    chunking\n\nphase 3 ->\n    convert each chunk into vector, this is done by our embedding models like LLM\n\nphase4 ->\n    store them in Vector DB(pinecone)\n\nHere we need to use diff diff things in each phase, for pdf we need to have pdf loader,\nfor chunking we should have chunking model, for converting each chunk into vector we need\nto use something else.\nWe can make them easy by using Langchain\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1qWvrzIMORJdyYjeH6Fer",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1317.9864865014686,
      "y": 81915.89094171129,
      "width": 132,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c00M",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1160519997,
      "version": 34,
      "versionNonce": 1875833107,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777709866946,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Langchain ->\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Langchain ->\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "okjul2r-67h1s1S_KdIA7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1357.4474240014686,
      "y": 81940.76594171129,
      "width": 1155,
      "height": 325,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c00N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1272480253,
      "version": 253,
      "versionNonce": 92582717,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1777710073867,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "It created utility function for use, by which above all process becomes easy. Langchain\nhas already prebuilt function those can uploade pdf, can do chunking, converting to vector\n\nLangChain is an open-source framework that simplifies building applications using large language models. \nIt helps developers connect LLMs with external data, tools and workflows and is available in both Python \nand JavaScript.\n\n\nHow LangChain Works?\nLangChain enables Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) by combining document processing, vector storage \nand LLMs to generate accurate, context aware responses. It connects embeddings, vector databases and \nmodels into a smooth workflow.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "It created utility function for use, by which above all process becomes easy. Langchain\nhas already prebuilt function those can uploade pdf, can do chunking, converting to vector\n\nLangChain is an open-source framework that simplifies building applications using large language models. \nIt helps developers connect LLMs with external data, tools and workflows and is available in both Python \nand JavaScript.\n\n\nHow LangChain Works?\nLangChain enables Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) by combining document processing, vector storage \nand LLMs to generate accurate, context aware responses. It connects embeddings, vector databases and \nmodels into a smooth workflow.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "d7YQ05wtzcbBZocYkBD5T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1283.5060177514686,
      "y": 81003.55500421129,
      "width": 11,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
